column5: Just heard the ships and ice breaker will be coming in. The last ship is due the 5 of January.
haha, your watching A channel.  Yesterday the freighter had to anchor and wait for the winds to die down. I could see it out the front window.
Hey,dont be giving away my sources.  Every bit helps kid.
Can't get anything pass you Brian !! Grain ship's been at the AGM dock since Christmas day ! lol... guess the stone boats comin in next !
I heard the sailors smoke "Seaweed" on the "Stoned" boats.
There was a lot of open water in Midland Bay this afternoon.  Tom
